== Introduction & Overview ==

== Download ==

An '''alpha'''-Version of BigStitcher is available via the Fiji Updater. Just go to {{bc | Help | Update...}}, click <code>Manage update sites</code> and select <code>BigStitcher</code> in the list. After applying the changes and restarting Fiji, BigStitcher will be available under {{bc | Plugins | BigStitcher | BigStitcher}}.

The source code is available {{GitHub|org=PreibischLab|repo=BigStitcher}}, please also report feature requests & bugs there.

